{"title":"十进制数转任意进制","date":"2025-08-27T07:06:00.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Aug 27, 2025","L":"08/27/2025","MM-DD":"08-27"},"author":"zmu","link":"2025/08/27/十进制数转任意进制","tags":["method"],"categories":["dev"],"updated":"2025-08-27T07:06:00.000Z","content":"<h1 id=\"十进制数转任意进制\">十进制数转任意进制<a title=\"#十进制数转任意进制\" href=\"#十进制数转任意进制\"></a></h1>\n<p>有时候碰到进制转换问题，这里提供一个公共方法，十进制转任意进制</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight c++\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 将十进制数字转换为指定进制（2-36）</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\">QString <span class=\"title\">toBase</span><span class=\"params\">(<span class=\"type\">int</span> number, <span class=\"type\">int</span> base)</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (number == <span class=\"number\">0</span>) <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"string\">&quot;0&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (base &lt; <span class=\"number\">2</span> || base &gt; <span class=\"number\">36</span>) <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> QString::<span class=\"built_in\">number</span>(number);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"type\">static</span> <span class=\"type\">const</span> <span class=\"type\">char</span> digits[] = <span class=\"string\">&quot;0123456789ABCDEFGHIJKLMNOPQRSTUVWXYZ&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    QString result; </span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">while</span> (number &gt; <span class=\"number\">0</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        result.<span class=\"built_in\">prepend</span>(digits[number % base]);</span><br><span class=\"line\">        number /= base;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> result;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>具体实现思路例子：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight tex\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">number = 25, base = 16</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">第一次循环:</span><br><span class=\"line\">  25 <span class=\"comment\">% 16 = 9 → digits[9] = &#x27;9&#x27;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  25 / 16 = 1</span><br><span class=\"line\">  result = &quot;9&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">第二次循环:</span><br><span class=\"line\">  1 <span class=\"comment\">% 16 = 1 → digits[1] = &#x27;1&#x27;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  1 / 16 = 0</span><br><span class=\"line\">  result = &quot;19&quot; (prepend所以是&quot;1&quot; + &quot;9&quot;)</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">结果: &quot;19&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n","next":{"title":"Kibana基本操作语法","link":"2025/08/26/Kibana基本操作语法"},"plink":"http://example.com/2025/08/27/十进制数转任意进制/","toc":[{"id":"十进制数转任意进制","title":"十进制数转任意进制","index":"1"}],"reading_time":"171 words in 1 min"}